title: Kammer Sieben - Contradictory Necrologues (2014) - FULL ALBUM
description:
In 2007 our first album was released, one year later we split. Some years passed, until we reunited in 2012. To celebrate with you, we decided to give away our latest work for free. 

Contradictory Necrologues gives you a new insight of Kammer Sieben's work. Haunting melodies, driven by electronic influences, let you dive deep into the new world of Kammer Sieben.
